<img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1805/442819.jpg" alt="Well-known radio personality Chris Gibbons joins Hot 91.9FM" width="220" height="147">Chris will be presenting the daily Business News on Joburg’s Hottest Breakfast at 07h40 and the daily round-up on the Big Joburg Drive 17h40 weekdays.Chris is one of South Africa’s best-known journalists as well as a sought-after public speaker, conference facilitator and media trainer.